OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPen Farthing: Watchdog has 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fno concerns over Afghan    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fanimal rescue              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A UK animal charity has been cleared of
OL,6, wrongdoing by a watchdog over its      
OL,7, fundraising effort to evacuate animals 
OL,8, from Afghanistan.                      
OL,10,FThe Charity Commission found no        
OL,11,Fregulatory concerns over Nowzad's      
OL,12,Fcampaign, known as Operation Ark.      
OL,14,FLed by founder Pen Farthing, the       
OL,15,Fcampaign raised more than #200,000 in  
OL,16,Fdays as the Taliban seized power.      
OL,18,FThe watchdog said the operation's      
OL,19,Fobjectives were made clear to donors   
OL,20,Fand trustees actions were reasonable.  
